description: Chicken, Steak or Veggie Kabobs drizzled with Teriyaki and YumYum sauces! Our Kabobs come with an assortment of fresh, colorful veggies which include: Red, Green, Yellow and Orange Peppers, Onions, Squash, Zucchini, Mushrooms and Cherry Tomatoes. We also have seasonal fruit kabobs, everyone's favorite Chicken and Waffle and Low Country Boil Kabobs. Everybody's asking, "What's on your Stick?"
name: King Kabob
